高齡者的衣物與穿著                      


  	What are the physical, psychological and social considerations in addressing the needs of the clothing and footwear for the elderly? What is adaptive clothing? Who is in needs of adaptive clothing and why? How to address the needs of adaptive clothing for the elderly? Where to get the help?

課程教育目標 

A. 培養理論與實務兼具之老年學專業B. 增進老年議題整合性思考與創新C. 提升獨立學習、掌握社會脈動與因應社會變遷之能力D. 啟發人文與社會關懷之熱忱E. 提升國際觀與國際視野 
